<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') -%>
<style>
/* Global Styles */
body {
    font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 81px;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f3f3f3;
}


.about-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px;
    background-color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
}

h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: #0099ff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

h2 {
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #444;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #0099ff;
    padding-bottom: 5px;
}

p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #666;
}

ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
}

ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}


.contact-info {
    background-color: #0099ff;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.contact-info li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
}

.contact-icon {
    margin-right: 10px;
    font-size: 24px;
}

.contact-info a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
}


@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
        padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
    }
}
 


</style>

<body>
    <div class="about-section">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our website! We are a passionate and dedicated team striving to provide the best services in our industry. Our mission is to make a positive impact on the lives of our customers and clients.</p>

        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>At our company, we envision a future where technology empowers people and businesses to achieve their full potential. We aim to lead the way in innovation and customer satisfaction.</p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to deliver high-quality products and services that exceed our customers' expectations. We are committed to fostering long-lasting relationships with our clients and creating a positive work environment for our employees.</p>

        <h2>Values</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Integrity: We believe in transparency, honesty, and ethical practices.</li>
            <li>Innovation: We continuously seek new ways to improve and adapt to the changing world.</li>
            <li>Customer Focus: Our customers' needs are at the heart of everything we do.</li>
            <li>Teamwork: We collaborate and support each other to achieve common goals.</li>
            <li>Excellence: We strive for excellence in all aspects of our business.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or inquiries, feel free to contact us:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: info@example.com</li>
            <li>Phone: +1 (123) 456-7890</li>
            <li>Address: 123 Main Street, City, Country</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
